---
title: Gametime Chicken Sausage & Pepper Subs with Mixed Green Salad & Balsamic Vinaigrette
description: Whether there’s a game on or not, we’re always on Team Melty Hot Subs. These sandwiches are made super easy with Italian chicken sausage, which already comes flecked with spices and packed with flavor. It’s cooked with bell peppers in a garlicky tomato sauce that gets a tangy boost from balsamic vinegar. Pile the filling into cute and crusty demi baguettes, then let a blanket of mozz melt over the subs. While they’re in the oven, prepare a quick salad to round out the meal. Just make sure your hands are sauce-free to receive all the high-fives for a winning dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/2021-w50-r14-gametime-chicken-sausage-pepper-subs-fc7dd76c.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/gametime-chicken-sausage-pepper-subs-6182a0b318f21856d4018d66-95dd1c0e.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/gametime-chicken-sausage-pepper-subs-6182a0b318f21856d4018d66
author: HelloFresh
course: main course
time required: 20m
nutrition:
  calories: 870 kcal
